        {
            "title": "在清淡的假日交易中 英國股市下跌 法國股市基本持平",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 英國股市小幅走低，法國股市基本持平，交易清淡，而歐洲多數主要股市因聖誕假期休市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國CAC 40指數基本持平，英國富時100指數下跌0.2%。兩個市場均僅進行半日交易，成交量低於平均水平。德國、義大利、丹麥、瑞士和芬蘭股市全天休市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，法國製藥巨頭賽諾菲股價下跌，此前該公司宣布美國食品藥品監督管理局對其多發性硬化癥實驗性藥物發出完整答復函。該法國藥企還同意以約22億美元收購Dynavax Technologies。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-88520373-8b68-3a5d-a37a-8baa7cf44269-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">BP公司股價收跌0.4%，此前該公司同意將其嘉實多業務中的多數股份出售給美國投資公司Stonepeak Partners，交易對業務估值（含債務）達101億美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u_UvK5RfldGAJiPD14U2Uw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a04a0a5f2d550344093e4a7f7af16166\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲斯托克600指數周二再創紀錄新高，在全球經濟成長前景持續樂觀及借貸成本走低的推動下，有望實現連續第三年上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞訊銀行高級分析師Ipek Ozkardeskaya表示，股市在年底最後幾天仍可能繼續上漲。「但之後呢？現實可能令人失望。科技市場部分板塊可能存在泡沫，明年財報季的焦點將不再是亮眼的數字，而是實際收入的來源。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題UK Stocks Dip, French Shares Subdued in Thin Holiday Trading</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Sagarika Jaisinghani.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%85%E6%B7%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%81%87%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E4%B8%AD-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%8C%81%E5%B9%B3-133932295.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-25 00:05:49",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國股指期貨徘徊於歷史高位附近 聖誕行情整裝待發",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fQA2a1fnGUN9_jfLPdbCdQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/90cb164057a408b11701fb8b7828281c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國股指期貨在聖誕假期前夕徘徊於歷史高位附近，股市季節性走強的時期即將開始。黃金價格攀升至每盎司4500美元以上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">紐約時間6:16，美國三大股指期貨基本持平。此前科技股推動標普500指數創下歷史新高。假期交易時間縮短，預計周三交投清淡。隨著聖誕行情拉開序幕，交易員們對年底收官持樂觀態度，可能使美國基準股指今年約17%的漲幅進一步擴大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國經濟持續超預期表現令投資者樂觀，支撐了來年的盈利前景。與此同時，貨幣市場仍預期聯儲會2026年至少降息兩次，這一背景可能提振更廣泛的股票板塊，儘管對領漲科技股估值的擔憂依然存在。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d7664a87-7644-32ca-967a-94c95b212d79-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Swissquote分析師Ipek Ozkardeskaya寫道：「近期行情表明聖誕老人或許仍會如約而至。但現實可能很快會占據上風，科技市場部分板塊看上去稍顯不穩，明年財報季的焦點將不再是亮眼的數字，而是關注收入的實際來源。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mk1agP7HY_RX.pn0GjHy2g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2ad9a971e0eec01159e6d359d467db3d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Stocks Hold Near Record High as Gold Powers Ahead: Markets Wrap</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E5%BE%98%E5%BE%8A%E6%96%BC%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91-%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E8%A1%8C%E6%83%85%E6%95%B4%E8%A3%9D%E5%BE%85%E7%99%BC-120153890.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-24 21:05:45",
