        {
            "title": "北京市進一步放寬購房政策 縮短購房者繳納個稅或社保的年限要求",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 北京市宣布放寬非本地戶籍居民購房限制，以提振持續低迷的房地產市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據周三發布的公告，北京市將縮短購房者關於繳納個人所得稅或社會保險的年限要求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些措施雖然不是全面放鬆購房限制，但標志著一系列穩定房地產市場的舉措又向前推進了一步。自去年五月推出全國性救助方案以來，由於銷售和價格自第二季度以來持續下滑，此番調整在此基礎上進一步推進。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於非北京戶籍家庭購買五環內商品住房，所需繳納個人所得稅或社保的年限將從三年縮短至兩年。對於購買五環外商品住房的，相關要求則從兩年縮短至一年。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1b09bbc1-0510-31fb-9911-ecbf11099589-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">北京市還為家庭提供更多靈活性。對二孩及以上的多子女居民家庭，在執行現有住房限購政策基礎上，可在五環內再多購買一套商品住房。借款申請人使用公積金貸款購買二套住房的，最低首付款比例由不低於30%調整為不低於25%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：標普將萬科評級下調至選擇性違約 認為境內債寬限期延長等同於違約</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Beijing City Further Relaxes Home-Buying Rules to Boost Sales</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Emma Dong.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B8%82%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E8%B3%BC%E6%88%BF%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96-%E7%B8%AE%E7%9F%AD%E8%B3%BC%E6%88%BF%E8%80%85%E7%B9%B3%E7%B4%8D%E5%80%8B%E7%A8%85%E6%88%96%E7%A4%BE%E4%BF%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B4%E9%99%90%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-102400469.html",
